### Customers

### Crear cliente válido
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "documentType": "CC",
  "documentNumber": "123456789",
  "firstName": "Carlos",
  "lastName": "Villamil",
  "email": "carlos@example.com",
  "phone": "3000000000",
  "birthDate": "1990-01-01"
}

### Intentar cliente menor de edad
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "documentType": "CC",
  "documentNumber": "987654321",
  "firstName": "Ana",
  "lastName": "Perez",
  "email": "ana@example.com",
  "phone": "3000000001",
  "birthDate": "2010-01-01"
}

### Listar clientes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers?page=0&size=20

### Accounts

### Crear cuenta de ahorro
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "UUID_DEL_CLIENTE",
  "accountType": "SAVINGS",
  "gmfExempt": false
}

### Crear cuenta corriente
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "UUID_DEL_CLIENTE",
  "accountType": "CHECKING",
  "gmfExempt": false
}

### Transactions

### Consignar
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/deposits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountNumber": "5300000001",
  "amount": 100000.00,
  "description": "Consignación"
}

### Retirar
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/withdrawals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountNumber": "5300000001",
  "amount": 50000.00,
  "description": "Retiro"
}

### Transferir
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/transfers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceAccountNumber": "5300000001",
  "destinationAccountNumber": "3300000001",
  "amount": 25000.00,
  "description": "Transferencia"
}

### Consultar transacción
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/UUID_DE_LA_TRANSACCION

### Account Statement

### Consultar estado de cuenta
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/number/5300000001/statement?startDate=2026-01-01T00:00:00&endDate=2026-12-31T23:59:59&page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc

### Cancelar cuenta con saldo cero
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/UUID_DE_LA_CUENTA/cancel

### Error cases

### Retiro sin fondos
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/withdrawals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountNumber": "5300000001",
  "amount": 9999999.99,
  "description": "Retiro sin fondos"
}

### Rango de fechas inválido
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/number/5300000001/statement?startDate=2026-12-31T23:59:59&endDate=2026-01-01T00:00:00&page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc